
4. Primary Screen Modules
I. My Companies (Dashboard)
Displays a list of all synced companies.
•	Columns: Company Name, Sync Status (Progress bar/Icon), Subscription Details.
•	Action: A "Go to Online" button/column that redirects the user to the Talliffy web portal for advanced data access.
 






II. Add Company
Used to link Tally data to the cloud.
•	Action: Clicking "Add" triggers the local-to-server sync function to fetch and upload data.

 









III. Settings (Tabbed Interface)
•	Tally Tab: Configure the Tally Connection Port.
•	Sync Tab: Configure Sync Interval Timings (e.g., every 30 mins, hourly).

 
